{"descriptions":[{"id":1263,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThe two constructions are expressed by placing \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་\u003c/span\u003e, which is derived from the literary form \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགྲབས་\u003c/span\u003e, after the main verb.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eTo say \u0026ldquo;to be about to,\u0026rdquo; Tibetan uses the existential auxiliaries \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡོད་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའདུག་\u003c/span\u003e, and \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་ཡོད་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་འདུག་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་ཡོད་\u003c/span\u003e (egophoric)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003e\u0026ldquo;To have just\u0026rdquo; is expressed by using the essential auxiliaries \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eརེད་\u003c/span\u003e or \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་རེད་\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་ཡིན་\u003c/span\u003e (egophoric)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eFinally, the verb \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eའགྲོའོ་\u003c/span\u003e may be followed by the verb \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eབྱེད་\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;to do\u0026rdquo;; this results in the meaning \u0026ldquo;all but\u0026rdquo; or \u0026ldquo;almost\u0026rdquo;:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཁྱེད་རང་ཞལ་ལག་མཆོད་འགྲོའོ་ཡོད་པས།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;Are you about to eat?\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཁོང་ཆུ་འདི་ནང་ལ་ཤི་འགྲོའོ་བྱེས་པ་རེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;He almost died in this river.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eགནམ་ཐང་ལ་སླེབས་འགྲོའོ་ཡོད་རེད།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;We\u0026rsquo;re about to arrive at the airport.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eང་འབྲུག་ཡུལ་ནས་ཡོང་འགྲོའོ་ཡིན།\u003c/span\u003e \u0026ldquo;I\u0026rsquo;ve just come from Bhutan.\u0026rdquo;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:22 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:22 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}